summary: Dynamic business professional with experience in the travel, events and FMCG industries. Special interest for educational travel, business development, outdoor education, sustainability and entrepreneurship. Currently studying part-time to become a certified French teacher at the Hogeschool in Rotterdam. International work and academic experiences acquired in Canada, The Netherlands, Bolivia, France and Austria. Speaks French, English and Dutch fluently. Passion for skiing, kayaking, canoeing and hiking. Becoming a mom is the most awesome thing that ever happened to me!
